{
  "message": "feat(conformance): add 8 linalg differential test cases for edge-case coverage\n\nExpand linalg_differential_cases.json with 8 new golden-value fixture\nentries targeting under-tested linear algebra edge cases:\n\n- linalg_solve_2x2_near_singular_stable (seed 8232): 2x2 solve with a\n  near-singular matrix (condition ~10000) in hardened mode, verifying\n  stable solution [1.0, 1.0] despite ill-conditioning.\n- linalg_solve_2x2_singular_error (seed 8233): 2x2 solve against an\n  exactly singular matrix [[1,2],[2,4]], expecting a singularity error\n  with reason code linalg_solver_singularity.\n- linalg_svd_2x2_runtime_high_condition_diagonal (seed 8234): SVD of a\n  diagonal matrix with condition number 1e12, asserting singular values\n  [1e6, 1e-6] within tolerance 1e-6.\n- linalg_qr_2x2_runtime_near_collinear_reconstruct (seed 8235): QR\n  decomposition of a near-collinear 2x2 matrix in hardened/reduced mode,\n  verifying Q is present and reconstruction tolerance holds.\n- linalg_lstsq_shapes_underdetermined_vector_rhs_3x5 (seed 8236): shape\n  contract for least-squares on an underdetermined 3x5 system with a\n  vector RHS, checking x_shape=[5], rank upper bound=3.\n- linalg_qr_shapes_reduced_wide_2x8 (seed 8237): shape contract for\n  reduced QR of a wide 2x8 matrix, expecting Q=[2,2] and R=[2,8].\n- linalg_svd_shapes_reduced_tall_9x2 (seed 8238): shape contract for\n  reduced SVD of a tall 9x2 matrix in hardened mode, expecting\n  U=[9,2], S=[2], Vh=[2,2].\n\nAll cases reference artifacts/phase2c/FNP-P2C-008/contract_table.md and\nuse env_fingerprint fnp-linalg-packet-f.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
